data.description: Mobile home on 433 with 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms sits on eleven acres that is all fenced in. In addition to the property it offers a HUGE metal building for storing cars, RV's, toys or can be used as a work shop. Mobile home is in fair condition, owner will not make any repairs or give any warranties and is being sold "AS-IS". Property does have electricity, water and a septic. This is perfect for anyone needing a get away home! The property is in a town that offers mostly agriculture, where farmers grow pistachios, alfalfa, livestock, and grapes. Also there is six ski lakes that you can enjoy fishing, boating, swimming, and waterskiing, or you have an option to hike, ride ATV's, horses or dirt bikes with the open space to go on a adventure and explore the wilderness. We are between the I-15 and I-40 about 25 min. past Barstow and two hours before Las Vegas, Laughlin and the Colorado River. Easy access to the freeway for whatever direction you choose to travel. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity.
